description: This app allows you to look up filehashes within VirusTotal. You need a valid VirusTotal API Key to use this app.

inputs.description: This should be a valid file hash such as MD5, SHA1, or SHA256
inputs.name: filehash

inputs.description:
This should be a valid VirusTotal API key. See the URI below to get APIKEY
https://www.virustotal.com/gui/user/<username>/apikey
inputs.name: apikey
